University ya <strong>Botswana</strong>, kapa '''UB''' e simolotswe ka ngwaga wa 1982 e le yone ya ntlha mo [[Botswana]]. University e e mo ditiropong tse nne tsa lefatshe la Botswana ebong  Maun, Francistown  le tse pedi mo Gaborone. E bo e nna le  makalana a le supa a thutego ebong,  Business, Education, Engineering, Humanities, Science le Social Sciences. Ya Faculty of Medicine e simolotse go tsaya bana ka ngwaga wa 2009 ka morago ga bokopano le ba University of Melbourne ko Australia..<ref>http://uninews.unimelb.edu.au/articleid_1252.html accessed 2008-09-18</ref>

